     C*                    Z-ADD0         J1HHAK
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    J1NOP
     C*
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    J1MSNS
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    J1MSZK
     C*更新日・者
     C*                    Z-ADD*YEAR     J1KOYY
     C*                    Z-ADDUMONTH    J1KOMM
     C*                    Z-ADDUDAY      J1KODD
     C*                    Z-ADDUJI       J1KOHH
     C*                    Z-ADDUFUN      J1KOSS
     C*                    MOVEL'AJSR42'  J1KOME
     C******************************
